---
title: Mango-Jerk Tofu Rice Bowls with Sweet Potatoes and Zesty Garlic-Lime Sauce
description: This island-inspired meal has all the bright and punchy flavours synonymous with Caribbean food! The best part? It's completely plant-based! Tender tofu, crisped-up then tossed in a flavourful jerk sauce, is served on a bed of fragrant basmati rice with roasted sweet potatoes. Finish it off with a drizzle of garlic-lime sauce!
